instruction: Generate a list of items necessary to go camping.
output:
Items necessary to go camping:
- Tent
- Sleeping bag
- Camping mattress
- Camping stove
- Cooking utensils
- Food
- Flashlight
- Battery pack
- Matches/lighter
- Matches and firewood
- Map or GPS
- First aid kit
- Bug spray
- Sunscreen
- Appropriate clothing
- Hiking boots
